# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Mobile app (safe to ship — anon key is public by design,
# protected by Row Level Security). NEVER put service-role or
# the football-data token here.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Edge Functions ONLY — set via `supabase secrets set ...`.
# Listed here for documentation; do NOT commit real values.
#   FOOTBALL_API_TOKEN  -> football-data.org API token
#   SUPABASE_URL        -> injected automatically in functions
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY -> injected automatically
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
